_sText: Smaller version of de_cathedrill_pro. Exactly this is original map with shorter nave (longer main hall) and shorter transept (both halls crossing longer main hall). I made this next version of map by request of FPSbanana member, who complained about size of map and low framerate. Gameplay is faster now and framerate was increased of a bit. I also removed horses in halls crossing, they didn't fit to theme of map, like someone complained with pro version. Enjoy my map
